casebody.data:
NEWARK UNIFIED SCHOOL DISTRICT
v.
S.C. (Brazil). No. S229112. Supreme Court of California May 11, 2016. CANTIL-SAKAUYE, C.J., WERDEGAR, CHIN, CORRIGAN, LIU, CUÉLLAR, and KRUGER, JJ., concur.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 1/1. Review in the above captioned matter, which was granted and held for Ardon v. City of Los Angeles (2016) 62 Cal.4th 1176 , 199 Cal.Rptr.3d 743 , 366 P.3d 996 , is hereby dismissed. (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(b)(1).) The opinion in this case is to remain published.
